# System Design

## Goal

Build a modular Retrieval-Augmented Generation application that allows users to upload documents and ask questions about them.

---

# High-Level Architecture

(User)

↓

(Frontend)

↓

(Backend API)

↓

(Document Service)

↓

(Retrieval Service)

↓

(LLM Service)

---

# Components

### Frontend

Responsibilities

- Upload documents
- Display chat
- Display answers
- Display sources

Input

- User interaction

Output

- HTTP requests

### Backend API

Responsibilities

- Receive requests
- Coordinate services
- Return responses

Input

- HTTP requests

Output

- JSON responses

### Document Service

Responsibilities

- Read PDF
- Extract text
- Store metadata

Input

- PDF

Output

- Plain text

### Chunking

Responsibilities

- Split text into chunks

Input

- Plain text

Output

- Text chunks

### Embedding Service

Responsibilities

- Generate embeddings

Input

- Text chunks

Output

- Vectors

### Vector Database

Responsibilities

- Store embeddings
- Retrieve similar vectors

Input

- Embeddings

Output

- Relevant chunks

### LLM Service

Responsibilities

- Generate answers

Input

- Question
- Retrieved chunks

Output

- Final answer
